// Section: Checking character class
// Function: is_lower()
// Synopsis: Returns true if all characters in the string are lowercase.
// Topics: Strings
// See Also: is_lower(), is_upper(), is_digit(), is_hexdigit(), is_letter()
// Usage:
//   x = is_lower(s);
